Name: Midnight Wonder Cup Noodles
AttributesDescription: Increases DEF and Max HP of all Resonators in the team by 10% and 20% respectively, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription:
Sepcially made by the Agronomy Wing, the cup noodles are famous for their rich aroma, which somehow manages to tempt people most at night. They may not be the most balanced meal, but they’re undeniably one of the academy’s favorites.

The container has its own heating system, so just add drinking water and wait. If left too long and the noodles or the vegetables start multiplying unusually fast, please contact the Agronomy Wing for collection.
